      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Cooltools leverages the widely-adopted cooler format which handles storage and access for high-resolution datasets. Cooler handles storage and access for high-resolution datasets via a sparse data model.",
      "asbval:note": "Confirmed: cooler is the storage format and library for Hi-C data.",
