      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The main cooltools modules were initially developed with mammalian interphase Hi-C maps in mind, but the flexible implementation of cooltools has made it useful for analysis of data from different organisms... Cooltools have been used to analyze Hi-C data across cell states, including mitosis and meiosis, and for organisms ranging from bacteria to yeast to invertebrates to mammals.",
