      "asbval:evidence_quote": "cooltools is open-source and structured to encourage future contributions... Cooltools provides detailed introductions to key concepts in Hi-C-data analysis with interactive notebook documentation... The Python API in cooltools yields interpretable and structured outputs (Pandas dataframes or Num Py arrays), facilitating both data exploration as well as future tool development.",
