      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The design of cooltools stems from its goal to enable flexible analyses of large quantities of high-resolution Hi-C data... Provide a modular set of tools with a balance between comprehensiveness and flexibility... Split the Python API into two layers: a high-level API for user-facing functions and a flexible low-level APIs... Cooltools provides detailed introductions to key concepts in Hi-C-data analysis with interactive notebook documentation.",
